OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of boy
OL,4,Ckilled by falling gravestone
OL,6,FHundreds of people have donated
OL,7,Ftowards funeral costs for a four-year-
OL,8,Fold boy killed in a "freak accident"
OL,9,Fwhen a gravestone fell on him in a
OL,10,Fcemetery.
OL,12,FThe youngster, who ITV News is
OL,13,Fchoosing not to name to respect his
OL,14,Ffamily's wishes, was at Rawtenstall
OL,15,FCemetery in Lancashire on Saturday, 5
OL,16,FJuly, when he was injured.
OL,18,FEmergency services were called but the
OL,19,Fboy could not be saved, Lancashire
OL,20,FPolice said.
