OL,6,FMore than 400 people have donated to a
OL,7,Ffundraiser on Go Fund Me, set up by
OL,8,Frelative, Donna Miller, to help pay
OL,9,Ffor the child's funeral.
OL,11,FMs Miller said his parents were
OL,12,F"devastated" to have lost their son in
OL,13,Fa "freak accident", adding: "All
OL,14,Fdonations no matter how small will
OL,15,Fhelp this young family massively and
OL,16,Fhelp them deal with this unexpected
OL,17,Ftragedy."
