OL,6,FIn a statement, Lancashire Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "As many of you are already
OL,8,Faware there was a tragic incident in
OL,9,FRawtenstall yesterday and we just
OL,10,Fwanted to give you the latest.
OL,12,F"We were called to Rawtenstall
OL,13,FCemetery at 1pm yesterday (July 5)
OL,14,Ffollowing reports a gravestone had
OL,15,Ffallen onto a child.
OL,17,F"Tragically, and despite the best
OL,18,Fefforts of the emergency services, the
OL,19,Fboy sadly died. Our thoughts are with
OL,20,Fhis loved ones at this devastating
OL,21,Ftime.
