OL,6,F"His death is not being treated as
OL,7,Fsuspicious and a file will be passed
OL,8,Fonto HM Coroner in due course."
OL,10,FThe police also added that the boy's
OL,11,Ffamily have requested privacy and that
OL,12,Fhe has not been named publicly to
OL,13,Frespect this wish.
OL,15,FRossendale Borough Council,
OL,16,Fresponsible for the cemetery in
OL,17,FRawtenstall, said in a statement: "We
OL,18,Fare deeply saddened by the tragic
OL,19,Fdeath of a young child at Rawtenstall
OL,20,FCemetery today.
